INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2013-03-13 18:24:25','2013-03-13 18:24:25','Welcome to WordPress. This is your first post. Edit or delete it, then start blogging!','Hello world!','','publish','open','open','','hello-world','','','2013-03-13 18:24:25','2013-03-13 18:24:25','',0,'http://completemarine.dev/?p=1',0,'post','',1),(2,1,'2013-03-13 18:24:25','2013-03-13 18:24:25','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\r\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\r\n...or something like this:\r\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\r\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://completemarine.dev/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Home','','publish','open','open','','sample-page','','','2013-03-13 19:47:37','2013-03-13 19:47:37','',0,'http://completemarine.dev/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0),(4,1,'2013-03-13 18:24:25','2013-03-13 18:24:25','This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"http://completemarine.dev/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!','Sample Page','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision','','','2013-03-13 18:24:25','2013-03-13 18:24:25','',2,'http://completemarine.dev/?p=4',0,'revision','',0),(5,1,'2013-03-13 19:47:43','2013-03-13 19:47:43','We offer Bayliner, Hurricane, Skeeter, Triton, and Yamaha. If you are new to boating, Bayliner offers a perfect balance of features and price. If you are looking for bass boats, recreational fishing boats, or a fish and ski boat, we recommend Skeeter and Triton. Hurricane is the leading deck boat in the industry and Yamahas are roomy and safe jet boats, perfect for watersports in general. You will find a wide variety of boats showcased in our large indoor showroom with a dedicated team of experts that can help you find the boat of your dreams.','New Boats','','publish','open','closed','','new-boats','','','2014-03-06 21:53:53','2014-03-06 21:53:53','',0,'http://completemarine.dev/?page_id=5',0,'page','',0),(6,1,'2013-03-13 19:47:49','2013-03-13 19:47:49','<p dir=\"ltr\">We sell a wide variety of used boats, ranging from fishing boats to watersport boats. Our clients feel confident when they purchase a used boat with Complete Marine, as our team of experts perform inspections on all boats. At Complete Marine we want to make sure our clients can buy the boat of their dreams in a way that fits within their budget. That’s why we offer financing options and trade-ins for clients to take advantage of. If you are interested in learning more about our finance options, give us a call at 480-966-1595 and we will walk you through the process.</p>\r\n&nbsp;','Used Boats','','publish','open','open','','used-boats','','','2014-03-06 22:41:46','2014-03-06 22:41:46','',0,'http://completemarine.dev/?page_id=6',0,'page','',0),(7,1,'2013-03-13 19:48:00','2013-03-13 19:48:00','Complete Marine has a large selection of WaveRunners, from single stand up personal watercraft to three seater luxury models. Complete Marine only sells the best products to our clients and we believe that Yamaha WaveRunners are the most reliable and highest quality personal water crafts on the market. Complete Marine has an indoor showroom displaying the wide selection of WaveRunners we offer, as well as a team of educated staff that are always available for questions and can help clients choose the best WaveRunner for all of their watersport needs and hobbies.','Wave Runners','','publish','open','closed','','wave-runners','','','2014-03-06 21:59:25','2014-03-06 21:59:25','',0,'http://completemarine.dev/?page_id=7',0,'page','',0),(8,1,'2013-03-13 19:48:08','2013-03-13 19:48:08','<p dir=\"ltr\">Complete Marine offers world class services from minor tune ups to major rebuilds. Complete Marine is able to perform expert repairs for boats, motors, and trailers, as well as outboard motors, inboards, sterndrives and jet drives. We also provide insurance estimates, as well as extended warranty and manufacturer warranty service. For clients who don’t want to deal with the hassle of selling their boat, we can sell their boat for them, or purchase it outright.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">As the weather starts to warm up, make sure your boat is ready to hit the water. Complete Marine\'s service team will make sure your boat is properly maintained and in top shape for boating season. To schedule a service appointment or for more information on the boating services and maintenance that we offer, call us at 480-966-1595 or drop off your boat at your convenience.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">If you are looking to repair your boat yourself and need a specific part, stop by our parts and accessories department, we stock parts for the major brands of outboard motors and sterndrives. We are also available and happy to help anyone needing advice or answers to their boating questions.</p>\r\n&nbsp;','Service','','publish','open','open','','service','','','2014-03-07 21:08:36','2014-03-07 21:08:36','',0,'http://completemarine.dev/?page_id=8',0,'page','',0),(9,1,'2013-03-13 19:48:14','2013-03-13 19:48:14','If you are looking for a specific part, we have an expert parts manager that can help you find exactly what it is you are looking for. From major parts to accessories, we carry high quality, genuine parts for your boat or motor. Our accessories range from stereos and boat ladders to electrical parts and steering systems. We carry an abundance of boat and motor parts and accessories, so that we are always prepared to meet our clients needs.\r\n\r\nWe are happy to help anyone wanting to repair their own boat and offer advice and answers to any questions our clients may have. Complete Marine also offers repairs for most makes and models of boats, motors and trailers, from tune-ups to full repairs, our trained staff can get your boat up and running again.\r\n\r\nCall for an appointment 480-966-1595 or simply drop your boat off at your convience. If you are looking for a specific part or accessory for your boat or motor, give us a call and we can provide you with the information and equipment you need.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Parts','','publish','open','open','','parts','','','2014-03-07 21:11:26','2014-03-07 21:11:26','',0,'http://completemarine.dev/?page_id=9',0,'page','',0),(10,1,'2013-03-13 19:48:22','2013-03-13 19:48:22','Complete Marine educates viewers on the different brands of boats that we offer and reviews details regarding boats, engines and interiors. We discuss which boats are best for our clients needs, hobbies, water sports, or recreational usage. Complete Marine has a wide variety of new and used boat brands that we sale, including: Bayliner, Hurricane, Skeeter, Triton, and Yamaha. We also offer WaveRunners that are high performing, durable, and sophisticated watercrafts, from single stand up’s to stadium seating jet ski’s. To view boats and WaveRunners that we have in stock, click here for a full overview.','Videos','','publish','open','open','','videos','','','2014-03-06 22:04:58','2014-03-06 22:04:58','',0,'http://completemarine.dev/?page_id=10',0,'page','',0),(11,1,'2013-03-13 19:48:51','2013-03-13 19:48:51',' ','','','publish','open','open','','11','','','2013-03-13 19:48:51','2013-03-13 19:48:51','',0,'http://completemarine.dev/?p=11',6,'nav_menu_item','',0),(12,1,'2013-03-13 19:48:51','2013-03-13 19:48:51',' ','','','publish','open','open','','12','','','2013-03-13 19:48:51','2013-03-13 19:48:51','',0,'http://completemarine.dev/?p=12',5,'nav_menu_item','',0),(13,1,'2013-03-13 19:48:51','2013-03-13 19:48:51',' ','','','publish','open','open','','13','','','2013-03-13 19:48:51','2013-03-13 19:48:51','',0,'http://completemarine.dev/?p=13',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(14,1,'2013-03-13 19:48:51','2013-03-13 19:48:51',' ','','','publish','open','open','','14','','','2013-03-13 19:48:51','2013-03-13 19:48:51','',0,'http://completemarine.dev/?p=14',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(15,1,'2013-03-13 19:48:51','2013-03-13 19:48:51',' ','','','publish','open','open','','15','','','2013-03-13 19:48:51','2013-03-13 19:48:51','',0,'http://completemarine.dev/?p=15',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(16,1,'2013-03-13 19:48:51','2013-03-13 19:48:51',' ','','','publish','open','open','','16','','','2013-03-13 19:48:51','2013-03-13 19:48:51','',0,'http://completemarine.dev/?p=16',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(20,1,'2013-06-21 14:46:03','2013-06-21 14:46:03','','Page Title Replacement','','publish','closed','closed','','acf_page-title-replacement','','','2013-06-21 14:46:03','2013-06-21 14:46:03','',0,'http://completemarine.dev/?pos